<div class="dora-avsmart-page">
  <div class="jumbotron hero Transcod">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="middle-container">
        <div class="row">
          <h2>
            <%= image_tag "banner/banner-transcoding-middle.png", class: "img", alt: "锐智转码 500 元优惠券 抢先领取", title: "锐智转码 500 元优惠券 抢先领取" -%>
          </h2>
          <h4>视频瘦身火热上线，成本与体验的合理配置，节省不止一点点&nbsp;<%= link_to raw("了解详情 &gt;&gt;"), "https://developer.qiniu.com/dora/manual/5135/avsmart", title: "数量有限 先到先得 了解详情", target: "_blank" -%></h4>
          <%= link_to "抢先领取", "", class: "btn btn-lg btn-default", title: "抢先领取", target: "", data: { toggle: "modal", target: "#dora-avsmart-apply-modal" } -%>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="body Transcoding">
    <div class="features">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="intro">
          <h2 class="title">
            <%= image_tag "dora_avsmart/img-transcoding-btl.png", alt: "产品亮点", title: "产品亮点" -%>
            产品亮点
            <%= image_tag "dora_avsmart/img-transcoding-btr.png", alt: "产品亮点", title: "产品亮点" -%>
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-6">
            <div class="media">
              <div class="media-left">
                <%= image_tag "dora_avsmart/img-transcoding-highlights1.png", class: "media-object", alt: "节省带宽", title: "节省带宽" -%>
              </div>
              <div class="media-body">
                <h4 class="media-heading">节省带宽</h4>
                <p>锐智转码融合感知编码、深度学习、图像处理、画质增强等技术，在保证画质的前提下，节省 20% 以上码率，为用户降低成本。</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-6">
            <div class="media">
              <div class="media-left">
                <%= image_tag "dora_avsmart/img-transcoding-highlights2.png", class: "media-object", alt: "视频编码技术", title: "视频编码技术" -%>
              </div>
              <div class="media-body">
                <h4 class="media-heading">视频编码技术</h4>
                <p>根据视频内容自适应码率以及自适应分辨率，不同场景可以适配最优的算法提升压缩和画质效果，追求最佳的收益效果。</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-6">
            <div class="media">
              <div class="media-left">
                <%= image_tag "dora_avsmart/img-transcoding-highlights3.png", class: "media-object", alt: "提升画质", title: "提升画质" -%>
              </div>
              <div class="media-body">
                <h4 class="media-heading">提升画质</h4>
                <p>AI 视频前处理包括：去编码脏效应、去燥、去毛刺、锐化、饱和度增强、去模糊等，并引入 Vmaf 和 Mos 质量评价体系，提升视频主观画质。</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-6">
            <div class="media">
              <div class="media-left">
                <%= image_tag "dora_avsmart/img-transcoding-highlights3.png", class: "media-object", alt: "精细处理", title: "精细处理" -%>
              </div>
              <div class="media-body">
                <h4 class="media-heading">精细处理</h4>
                <p>ROI 感兴趣区域识别：包括人脸、人眼聚焦、前景重点区域、及各个块的主观敏感度，对用户关注区域进行动态编码。</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="features features-dora-avsmart-progress d-none">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="Transcoding-Progress">
          <p class="title">距离活动结束还有</p>
          <div class="clear"></div>
          <div id="dora-avsmart-progress"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="features">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="intro">
          <h2 class="title">
            <%= image_tag "dora_avsmart/img-transcoding-btl.png", alt: "如何参与", title: "如何参与" -%>
